snippet.title: Dogfights in SLZ · Free Game · Showcase
snippet.description:
Link to play: https://www.newgrounds.com/portal/view/886449
Dogfights in SLZ is a fast-paced shoot-em-up game. Dominate the sky, destroy enemies and survive for as long as you can. Press [Space] to start the game.

Credits:

• Wired Dreams Studio: https://wireddreamsstudio.newgrounds.com/
